(i) Create conda environment
Command: conda create -n sp --clone base

(ii) Activate the conda environment
Command: conda activate sp

(iii) Install Spacy
Command: conda install -c conda-forge spacy

(iv) Test the installation
Command: python -c "import os; import spacy; print(os.path.dirname(spacy.__file__))"

(v) Deactivate the environment to go to base environment
Command: conda deactivate
